r />\n<br />\n<br />\n再借個位<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T12:49:23.000Z","msg":"你地講就冇事，我講就次次比人屈毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />明明個諗法同我一樣"},{"pid":"42814064d3089a28889de64a4d5c3ddb961570c8","tid":2031374,"uid":95,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"78d425f11670d0f7e24702bef78f3af7ae96d6ae","tid":2031374,"uid":308251,"like":23,"dislike":243,"score":-220,"citedBy":17,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T11:03:41.000Z","msg":"咪戇尻啦，佢地入獄先回響大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T12:51:11.000Z","msg":"你咁講咪即係坐監令人生更精彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59aa6329e6e8e1b9a36315141618e7faea42ce2a","tid":2031374,"uid":38316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T12:51:59.000Z","msg":"唔好喺連登度講，直接FB佢啦"},{"pid":"81d960713c67a2f56659e269e6f6955482b2b976","tid":2031374,"uid":327767,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T12:52:26.000Z","msg":"走，仲可以無海外發聲；<br />\n唔走=劉曉波<br />\n<br />\n叫佢留低果班，因為頭上有國際光環就要人以死鳴志換國際關注，之前有一大班手足被捕、犧牲所以Gphone明知死硬都要留低陪葬又係咩玩法？抗爭就唔洗講良心？"},{"pid":"df89ceb87baa152d9cfad00a55cacb9d6c489324","tid":2031374,"uid":308251,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"42814064d3089a28889de64a4d5c3ddb961570c8","tid":2031374,"uid":95,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"78d425f11670d0f7e24702bef78f3af7ae96d6ae","tid":2031374,"uid":308251,"like":23,"dislike":243,"score":-220,"citedBy":17,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T11:03:41.000Z","msg":"咪戇尻啦，佢地入獄先回響大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T12:51:11.000Z","msg":"你咁講咪即係坐監令人生更精彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"